            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Deae Fortu<lb break="no" n="2"/>nae sacrum <lb n="3"/>Sempronius <lb n="4"/>Martialis <expan><abbr>praef</abbr><ex>ectus</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>otum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>olvit</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibens</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>aetus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erito</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Fortunagruppe mit Weihung; Oberteil stark fragmentiert, Schriftfeld in Basis mit peltaförmigen ansae. Z. 4: TI-, RA-Ligaturen. (B): Z. 4: pref(ectus). Autopsie R. Wiegels; Hauptbearbeiterin: B. Esch.</p>
            </div>
